US News and World Report</link> Graduate School rankings, the Heinz School was ranked 10th overall among <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../993/5630993.xml">
schools of public affairs</link>. Of the 253 schools of public affairs across the nation that were surveyed, the Heinz School ranked:</p>
