<entry level="1" type="bullet">

4th in Public Policy Analysis;</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

10th in Environmental Policy and Management;</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

10th in Health Policy and Management.</entry>
</list>
</p>
<p>

The Heinz School also ranked 2nd in the <body wordnetid="107965085" confidence="0.8">
<university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.8">
<social_group wordnetid="107950920" confidence="0.8">
<group wordnetid="100031264" confidence="0.8">
